Package ionic.Msmq

Class Summary
Message The Message class models a message that is sent to or receive from an MSMQ queue.
Queue The Queue class represents a message queue in MSMQ.
 

Enum Summary
Queue.Access The Queue.Access enum provides options for access to the MSMQ Queue: Either Receive, Send, or both.
TransactionType Specifies the transaction type to use when enqueuing messages into a transactional queue.
 

Exception Summary
MessageQueueException An exception type to wrap any problems that occur during MSMQ operations.
